tFileManager

Class TFiles

  • java.lang.Object
    • tFileManager.TFiles

  • public class TFiles
extends java.lang.Object
    Handles composing and parsing of list/map-based information to Strings

    eg: values58123A44 B44 C125
    eg: values58123a58alice, b58bob, x58123A44 B44 C125125

    Author:
    Tallon Hodge
